--- Dependencies ---

Ignore node_modules folders in both backend and frontend

backend/node_modules/
frontend/node_modules/

--- Environment Variables ---

Ignore the .env file in the backend

backend/.env

--- Build Output (Vite Frontend) ---

Ignore the production build folder created by 'npm run build' in frontend

frontend/build/

Ignore Vite's cache directory

frontend/.vite/

--- Logs ---

Ignore general log files and npm/yarn specific logs

.log
npm-debug.log
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

--- Operating System Files ---

Ignore macOS specific files

.DS_Store

Ignore Windows specific files

Thumbs.db

--- IDE/Editor Specific Files ---

Ignore VS Code specific settings/cache

.vscode/

Ignore JetBrains IDE specific files (WebStorm, IntelliJ IDEA, etc.)

.idea/

--- Other ---

Ignore temporary files or potential sensitive files if generated

*.tmp
*.swp